OL,3,CWhy has this motorway been named the
OL,4,Cworst in England?
OL,6,FThe M42 is the worst motorway in the
OL,7,FUK, according to a recent survey.
OL,9,FThe 40-mile-long motorway connects
OL,10,FNottingham, Solihull, Tamworth and
OL,11,FRedditch.
OL,13,FOne survey respondent criticised the
OL,14,FM42's "roadworks, potholes and
OL,15,Fdelays", describing the motorway as a
OL,16,F"terrible road to drive on".
