OL,3,CWhy has this motorway been named the
OL,4,Cworst in England?
OL,6,FAnother said variable speed limits "do
OL,7,Fnot always reflect the traffic
OL,8,Fconditions", complaining that they
OL,9,Fwere "directed to reduce speed for no
OL,10,Fapparent reason".
OL,12,FThe survey by watchdog Transport Focus
OL,13,Fgot 9,166 road users to review
OL,14,Fmotorways based on user experience.
OL,16,FThe poll was carried out in the year
OL,17,Fto the end of March, coinciding with
OL,18,Fmajor roadworks on the M42 around
OL,19,FBirmingham Airport.
OL,21,FWhich motorway was named the best ?
